<AddOnInstructionDefinition Name="pump_run_status_indicate" Revision="1.0" ExecutePrescan="false" ExecutePostscan="false" ExecuteEnableInFalse="false" CreatedDate="2024-04-18T01:06:03.821Z" CreatedBy="DESKTOP-EB2DFQ8\wymwym" EditedDate="2024-09-02T13:25:03.075Z" EditedBy="PC-XINGUANG\wymwym" SoftwareRevision="v34.00">
<Description>
<![CDATA[指示泵运行/停止状态：
