</DefaultData>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="ModbusData" TagType="Base" DataType="raC_UDT_ModbusClientData" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false"/>
<Parameter Name="CommandString" TagType="Base" DataType="STR0500" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false"/>
</Parameters>
<LocalTags>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_BufferByteIndex" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_Cmd_Last" DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_Index" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_BufferBitIndex" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_ArraySize" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
</LocalTags>
<Routines>
<Routine Name="Logic" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[This routine unpacks the reply data for binary read operations and writes the data to the local arrays.

Check for a valid response length in bits.
Currently limited to 256, but can be increased]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIO(Inputs) MOV(1024,Wrk_ArraySize) ,XIC(Inputs) MOV(1024,Wrk_ArraySize) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LES(Modbus_CMD_Len,1)GRT(Modbus_CMD_Len,256)JMP(end1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Set up and call the _SUB_0x_WR function and call it to unpack the data and write it into the local data arrays at the LocalOffset specified in the transaction.
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[MOV(2,Wrk_BufferByteIndex)MOV(0,Wrk_BufferBitIndex)SUB(Modbus_CMD_Len,1,Wrk_Cmd_Last)ADD(Wrk_Cmd_Last,LocalOffset,Wrk_Cmd_Last)MOV(LocalOffset,Wrk_Index);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[GEQ(Wrk_Cmd_Last,Wrk_ArraySize)JMP(end1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Here is where the data is written locally.]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[LBL(Loop)XIC(CommandString.DATA[Wrk_BufferByteIndex].[Wrk_BufferBitIndex])[XIO(Inputs) OTL(ModbusData.Coils_0xxx[Wrk_Index]) ,XIC(Inputs) OTL(ModbusData.DiscInputs_1xxx[Wrk_Index]) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(CommandString.DATA[Wrk_BufferByteIndex].[Wrk_BufferBitIndex])[XIO(Inputs) OTU(ModbusData.Coils_0xxx[Wrk_Index]) ,XIC(Inputs) OTU(ModbusData.DiscInputs_1xxx[Wrk_Index]) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[ADD(Wrk_BufferBitIndex,1,Wrk_BufferBitIndex)GRT(Wrk_BufferBitIndex,7)CLR(Wrk_BufferBitIndex)ADD(Wrk_BufferByteIndex,1,Wrk_BufferByteIndex);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LES(Wrk_Index,Wrk_Cmd_Last)ADD(Wrk_Index,1,Wrk_Index)JMP(Loop);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LBL(end1)NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="Prescan" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[CLR(Wrk_BufferByteIndex)CLR(Wrk_BufferBitIndex)CLR(Wrk_Index);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
</AddOnInstructionDefinition>
<AddOnInstructionDefinition Name="raC_Tec_NetModbusTCPClient_RespStrWord" Revision="2.0" ExecutePrescan="true" ExecutePostscan="false" ExecuteEnableInFalse="false" CreatedDate="2019-12-09T12:11:37.717Z" CreatedBy="Not Available" EditedDate="2024-09-02T13:25:04.381Z" EditedBy="PC-XINGUANG\wymwym" SoftwareRevision="v34.00">
<Parameters>
<Parameter Name="EnableIn" TagType="Base" DataType="BOOL" Usage="Input" Radix="Decimal" Required="false" Visible="false" ExternalAccess="Read Only">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Enable Input - System Defined Parameter]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="EnableOut" TagType="Base" DataType="BOOL" Usage="Output" Radix="Decimal" Required="false" Visible="false" ExternalAccess="Read Only">
<Description>
<![CDATA[Enable Output - System Defined Parameter]]>
</Description>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="Reg3xx" TagType="Base" DataType="BOOL" Usage="Input" Radix="Decimal" Required="true" Visible="true" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="BOOL" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="Modbus_CMD_Len" TagType="Base" DataType="INT" Usage="Input" Radix="Decimal" Required="true" Visible="true" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="LocalOffset" TagType="Base" DataType="INT" Usage="Input" Radix="Decimal" Required="true" Visible="true" ExternalAccess="Read/Write">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</Parameter>
<Parameter Name="ModbusData" TagType="Base" DataType="raC_UDT_ModbusClientData" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false"/>
<Parameter Name="CommandString" TagType="Base" DataType="STR0500" Usage="InOut" Required="true" Visible="true" Constant="false"/>
</Parameters>
<LocalTags>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_StringPosition" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_Cmd_Last" DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_Temp_Int" DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="INT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
<LocalTag Name="Wrk_Index" DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" ExternalAccess="None">
<DefaultData Format="L5K">
<![CDATA[0]]>
</DefaultData>
<DefaultData Format="Decorated">
<DataValue DataType="DINT" Radix="Decimal" Value="0"/>
</DefaultData>
</LocalTag>
</LocalTags>
<Routines>
<Routine Name="Logic" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Called from Packet_Processing to parse register data and write it to the local arrays .

First Check the range of registers to make sure we're within specified limits.
Length is limited to 120]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LES(Modbus_CMD_Len,1)GRT(Modbus_CMD_Len,120)JMP(end1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Set up values for the _Sub_4x_WR routine.  Starting position and length.
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[MOV(2,Wrk_StringPosition)SUB(Modbus_CMD_Len,1,Wrk_Cmd_Last)ADD(Wrk_Cmd_Last,LocalOffset,Wrk_Cmd_Last)MOV(LocalOffset,Wrk_Index);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LBL(Loop)COP(CommandString.DATA[Wrk_StringPosition],Wrk_Temp_Int,1)[XIO(Reg3xx) SWPB(Wrk_Temp_Int,REVERSE,ModbusData.HoldRegisters_4xxx[Wrk_Index]) ,XIC(Reg3xx) SWPB(Wrk_Temp_Int,REVERSE,ModbusData.InpRegisters_3xxx[Wrk_Index]) ]ADD(Wrk_StringPosition,2,Wrk_StringPosition);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LES(Wrk_Index,Wrk_Cmd_Last)ADD(Wrk_Index,1,Wrk_Index)JMP(Loop);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[LBL(end1)NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="Prescan" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[CLR(Wrk_Index);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
