<![CDATA[The last recorded socket error for this connection.  
0  good, 
-2 Write Error, 
-4 Read Error,
-6 connection failed, 
-7 Delete all failed, 
-8 Create Soc failed, 
-9 Connection failed, -10 connection dropped, -11 error in setting socket parameter.
-12 - Enable removed]]>
