<Routine Name="flow_deviation_PAC" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[流量计、数字泵反馈的流量数值，如果偏差大于设定值，则自动触发系统偏流报警。]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1号泵组流量偏差判断]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[flow_deviation(PAC_flow_deviation_1,PAC_flow_deviation,P_PAC1_flow_read,P_PAC2_flow_read,PAC_flow_8FT01,P_PAC1_run,P_PAC2_run,pump_flow_deviation_temp[1],pump_flow_deviation_temp[2],meter_flow_deviation_temp[1],P_PAC1_flow_set,P_PAC2_flow_set);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2号泵组流量偏差判断]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[flow_deviation(PAC_flow_deviation_2,PAC_flow_deviation,P_PAC3_flow_read,P_PAC4_flow_read,PAC_flow_8FT02,P_PAC3_run,P_PAC4_run,pump_flow_deviation_temp[3],pump_flow_deviation_temp[4],meter_flow_deviation_temp[2],P_PAC3_flow_set,P_PAC4_flow_set);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#流量计偏流报警延时]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(meter_flow_deviation_temp[1])XIO(PAC_flow_reset_8FT01)TON(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[0],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#流量计偏流报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[0].DN)OTE(PAC_flow_err_8FT01);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#流量计偏流报警延时]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(meter_flow_deviation_temp[2])XIO(PAC_flow_reset_8FT02)TON(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[1],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#流量计偏流报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[1].DN)OTE(PAC_flow_err_8FT02);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#数字泵偏流报警延时]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(pump_flow_deviation_temp[1])XIO(P_PAC1_reset)TON(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[2],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#数字泵偏流报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[2].DN)OTE(P_PAC1_flow_err);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#数字泵偏流报警延时]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(pump_flow_deviation_temp[2])XIO(P_PAC2_reset)TON(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[3],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#数字泵偏流报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[3].DN)OTE(P_PAC2_flow_err);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="10" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#数字泵偏流报警延时]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(pump_flow_deviation_temp[3])XIO(P_PAC3_reset)TON(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[4],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="11" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#数字泵偏流报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[4].DN)OTE(P_PAC3_flow_err);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="12" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4#数字泵偏流报警延时]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(pump_flow_deviation_temp[4])XIO(P_PAC4_reset)TON(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[5],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="13" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4#数字泵偏流报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_flow_deviation_timer[5].DN)OTE(P_PAC4_flow_err);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="14" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[聚铝1号加药装置2泵同时故障]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(P_PAC1_err)XIC(P_PAC2_err)OTE(two_pumps_error[1]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="15" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[聚铝2号加药装置2泵同时故障]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(P_PAC3_err)XIC(P_PAC4_err)OTE(two_pumps_error[2]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="MainRoutine" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[PAC系统4-20mA输入输出参数重置为默认值。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(analog_IO_setting_reset[1])JSR(analog_IO_setting_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[将I/O输入的数值，同步到系统变量，方便触摸屏及上位机读取]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(synchronize_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[将4个PAC池当前液位，与液位过高报警值、液位过低报警值对照，如果液位过高、过低，则发出报警。
如果液位过高，则自动关闭进液阀。如果液位过低，则自动关闭出液位。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(tank_control_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[数字泵的启动/停止控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(pump_action_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[计算各数字泵投加流量，并传到相关AO模块输出。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(YaoHao_flow_set_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[阀门动作控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(valve_action_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[搅拌机控制程序]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(mixer_action_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[判断数字泵反馈流量与流量计反馈流量是否存在偏差。
如果偏差值大于30%，且持续60秒以上，则触发偏流报警。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(flow_deviation_PAC,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="mixer_action_PAC" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[搅拌机启动/停止]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[设置搅拌机运行/间歇时间]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[1],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[1].PRE) MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[2],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[2].PRE) MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[3],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[5].PRE) MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[4],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[6].PRE) ,MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[1],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[3].PRE) MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[2],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[4].PRE) MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[3],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[7].PRE) MUL(PAC_stirrer_time_setting[4],60000,PAC_stirrer_timer[8].PRE) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池，设为自动切换时，2台搅拌机轮流运行。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_tank_auto_manual[1])[ONS(PAC_stirrer_one_shot[1]) [OTL(MI_PAC1_actuate) ,OTL(stirrer_working[1]) ,OTU(stirrer_working[2]) ,OTU(MI_PAC2_actuate) ] ,XIC(MI_PAC1_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC2_actuate) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[1],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[1].DN) OTU(MI_PAC1_actuate) ,XIO(MI_PAC1_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC2_actuate) XIC(stirrer_working[1]) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[2],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[2].DN) [OTU(stirrer_working[1]) ,OTL(stirrer_working[2]) ,OTL(MI_PAC2_actuate) ] ,XIC(MI_PAC2_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC1_actuate) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[3],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[3].DN) OTU(MI_PAC2_actuate) ,XIO(MI_PAC1_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC2_actuate) XIC(stirrer_working[2]) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[4],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[4].DN) [OTU(stirrer_working[2]) ,OTL(stirrer_working[1]) ,OTL(MI_PAC1_actuate) ] ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#PAC池，设为自动切换时，2台搅拌机轮流运行。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_tank_auto_manual[2])[ONS(PAC_stirrer_one_shot[2]) [OTL(MI_PAC3_actuate) ,OTL(stirrer_working[3]) ,OTU(stirrer_working[4]) ,OTU(MI_PAC4_actuate) ] ,XIC(MI_PAC3_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC4_actuate) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[5],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[5].DN) OTU(MI_PAC3_actuate) ,XIO(MI_PAC3_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC4_actuate) XIC(stirrer_working[3]) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[6],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[6].DN) [OTU(stirrer_working[3]) ,OTL(stirrer_working[4]) ,OTL(MI_PAC4_actuate) ] ,XIC(MI_PAC4_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC3_actuate) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[7],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[7].DN) OTU(MI_PAC4_actuate) ,XIO(MI_PAC3_actuate) XIO(MI_PAC4_actuate) XIC(stirrer_working[4]) TON(PAC_stirrer_timer[8],?,?) ,XIC(PAC_stirrer_timer[8].DN) [OTU(stirrer_working[4]) ,OTL(stirrer_working[3]) ,OTL(MI_PAC3_actuate) ] ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池，搅拌机控制由自动切换为手动时，搅拌机都先停机，等待手动指令决定是否开机。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(PAC_tank_auto_manual[1])ONS(PAC_stirrer_one_shot[11])[OTU(MI_PAC1_actuate) ,OTU(MI_PAC2_actuate) ,OTU(MI_PAC_actuate_local[1]) ,OTU(MI_PAC_actuate_local[2]) ,OTU(stirrer_working[1]) ,OTU(stirrer_working[2]) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池，搅拌机控制由自动切换为手动时，搅拌机都先停机，等待手动指令决定是否开机。]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(PAC_tank_auto_manual[2])ONS(PAC_stirrer_one_shot[12])[OTU(MI_PAC3_actuate) ,OTU(MI_PAC4_actuate) ,OTU(MI_PAC_actuate_local[3]) ,OTU(MI_PAC_actuate_local[4]) ,OTU(stirrer_working[3]) ,OTU(stirrer_working[4]) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(MI_PAC1_actuate)OTE(RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(MI_PAC2_actuate)OTE(RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.1);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(MI_PAC3_actuate)OTE(RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.2);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(MI_PAC4_actuate)OTE(RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.3);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="pump_action_PAC" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[控制数字泵的启动/停止]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#数字泵控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[pump_start_stop_PAC(PAC_pump_action_1,PAC_valve_timer[0].DN,VE_PAC_07_close,VE_PAC_08_close,VE_PAC_09_close,VE_PAC_10_close,VE_PAC_01_close,P_PAC_actuate_local[1],RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.4,P_PAC1_maintain,P_PAC1_err,P_PAC1_actuate,PAC_control_local_remote[1],P_PAC2_err,P_PAC2_maintain);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#数字泵控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[pump_start_stop_PAC(PAC_pump_action_2,PAC_valve_timer[0].DN,VE_PAC_07_close,VE_PAC_08_close,VE_PAC_09_close,VE_PAC_10_close,VE_PAC_02_close,P_PAC_actuate_local[2],RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.5,P_PAC2_maintain,P_PAC2_err,P_PAC2_actuate,PAC_control_local_remote[1],P_PAC1_err,P_PAC1_maintain);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#数字泵控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[pump_start_stop_PAC(PAC_pump_action_3,PAC_valve_timer[0].DN,VE_PAC_07_close,VE_PAC_08_close,VE_PAC_09_close,VE_PAC_10_close,VE_PAC_03_close,P_PAC_actuate_local[3],RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.6,P_PAC3_maintain,P_PAC3_err,P_PAC3_actuate,PAC_control_local_remote[2],P_PAC4_err,P_PAC4_maintain);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4#数字泵控制]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[pump_start_stop_PAC(PAC_pump_action_4,PAC_valve_timer[0].DN,VE_PAC_07_close,VE_PAC_08_close,VE_PAC_09_close,VE_PAC_10_close,VE_PAC_04_close,P_PAC_actuate_local[4],RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.7,P_PAC4_maintain,P_PAC4_err,P_PAC4_actuate,PAC_control_local_remote[2],P_PAC3_err,P_PAC3_maintain);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4个PAC池出液阀全部关到位，则报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(VE_PAC_07_close)XIC(VE_PAC_08_close)XIC(VE_PAC_09_close)XIC(VE_PAC_10_close)OTE(PAC_tank_valve_alarm);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4个PAC池出液阀全部关到位报警持续超过30秒，则停泵]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(PAC_tank_valve_alarm)TON(PAC_valve_timer[0],?,?);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1号泵故障时切换至2号泵]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(P_PAC1_err)XIO(P_PAC1_maintain)XIC(P_PAC1_actuate)ONS(PAC_pump_one_shot[1])[OTU(P_PAC1_actuate) ,OTU(P_PAC_actuate_local[1]) ,OTL(P_PAC_actuate_local[2]) ,OTL(P_PAC2_actuate) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2号泵故障时切换至1号泵]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(P_PAC2_err)XIO(P_PAC2_maintain)XIC(P_PAC2_actuate)ONS(PAC_pump_one_shot[2])[OTU(P_PAC2_actuate) ,OTU(P_PAC_actuate_local[2]) ,OTL(P_PAC_actuate_local[1]) ,OTL(P_PAC1_actuate) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3泵故障时切换至4号泵]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(P_PAC3_err)XIO(P_PAC3_maintain)XIC(P_PAC3_actuate)ONS(PAC_pump_one_shot[3])[OTU(P_PAC3_actuate) ,OTU(P_PAC_actuate_local[3]) ,OTL(P_PAC_actuate_local[4]) ,OTL(P_PAC4_actuate) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4号泵故障时切换至3号泵]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(P_PAC4_err)XIO(P_PAC4_maintain)XIC(P_PAC4_actuate)ONS(PAC_pump_one_shot[4])[OTU(P_PAC4_actuate) ,OTU(P_PAC_actuate_local[4]) ,OTL(P_PAC_actuate_local[3]) ,OTL(P_PAC3_actuate) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="10" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[流量反馈值与设定值偏差超过20%报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[GRT(P_PAC1_flow_set,0.0)CPT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[1],(P_PAC1_flow_read-P_PAC1_flow_set)/P_PAC1_flow_set)ABS(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[1],PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[1])GRT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[1],0.2)XIC(P_PAC1_run)OTE(PAC_pump_flow_deviation[1]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="11" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[流量反馈值与设定值偏差超过20%报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[GRT(P_PAC2_flow_set,0.0)CPT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[2],(P_PAC2_flow_read-P_PAC2_flow_set)/P_PAC2_flow_set)ABS(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[2],PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[2])GRT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[2],0.2)XIC(P_PAC2_run)OTE(PAC_pump_flow_deviation[2]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="12" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[流量反馈值与设定值偏差超过20%报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[GRT(P_PAC3_flow_set,0.0)CPT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[3],(P_PAC3_flow_read-P_PAC3_flow_set)/P_PAC3_flow_set)ABS(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[3],PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[3])GRT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[3],0.2)XIC(P_PAC3_run)OTE(PAC_pump_flow_deviation[3]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="13" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[流量反馈值与设定值偏差超过20%报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[GRT(P_PAC4_flow_set,0.0)CPT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[4],(P_PAC4_flow_read-P_PAC4_flow_set)/P_PAC4_flow_set)ABS(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[4],PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[4])GRT(PAC_pump_flow_deviation_value[4],0.2)XIC(P_PAC4_run)OTE(PAC_pump_flow_deviation[4]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="synchronize_PAC" Type="ST">
<Description>
<![CDATA[同步I/O输入的数值。]]>
</Description>
<STContent>
<Line Number="0">
<![CDATA[(*搅拌机运行状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="1">
<![CDATA[MI_PAC1_run:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="2">
<![CDATA[MI_PAC2_run:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="3">
<![CDATA[MI_PAC3_run:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.2;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="4">
<![CDATA[MI_PAC4_run:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.3;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="5">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="6">
<![CDATA[(*稀释加压泵运行状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="7">
<![CDATA[(*软水加压泵运行状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="8">
<![CDATA[pressure_pump_run[1]:=RemoteIO1:1:I.Data.8;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="9">
<![CDATA[(*生产用水加压泵运行状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="10">
<![CDATA[pressure_pump_run[2]:=RemoteIO1:1:I.Data.9;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="11">
<![CDATA[(*软水加压泵故障状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="12">
<![CDATA[pressure_pump_run[11]:=RemoteIO1:1:I.Data.8;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="13">
<![CDATA[(*生产用水加压泵故障状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="14">
<![CDATA[pressure_pump_run[12]:=RemoteIO1:1:I.Data.9;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="15">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="16">
<![CDATA[(*数字泵运行状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="17">
<![CDATA[pump_run_status_indicate(pump_run_status_indicate_1,RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.4,P_PAC1_flow_read,P_PAC1_run);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="18">
<![CDATA[pump_run_status_indicate(pump_run_status_indicate_2,RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.5,P_PAC2_flow_read,P_PAC2_run);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="19">
<![CDATA[pump_run_status_indicate(pump_run_status_indicate_3,RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.6,P_PAC3_flow_read,P_PAC3_run);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="20">
<![CDATA[pump_run_status_indicate(pump_run_status_indicate_4,RemoteIO1:2:O.Data.7,P_PAC4_flow_read,P_PAC4_run);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="21">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="22">
<![CDATA[(*流量计偏流报警时、或通讯故障时自动切换到检修状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="23">
<![CDATA[if PAC_flow_err_8FT01 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="24">
<![CDATA[	PAC_flow_maintain_8FT01:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="25">
<![CDATA[	end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="26">
<![CDATA[if PAC_flow_err_8FT02 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="27">
<![CDATA[	PAC_flow_maintain_8FT02:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="28">
<![CDATA[	end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="29">
<![CDATA[	]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="30">
<![CDATA[(*流量计故障复位时，检修状态及偏流状态同时复位*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="31">
<![CDATA[if PAC_flow_reset_8FT01 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="32">
<![CDATA[	PAC_flow_maintain_8FT01:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="33">
<![CDATA[	end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="34">
<![CDATA[if PAC_flow_reset_8FT02 then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="35">
<![CDATA[	PAC_flow_maintain_8FT02:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="36">
<![CDATA[	end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="37">
<![CDATA[	]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="38">
<![CDATA[(*数字泵故障状态*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="39">
<![CDATA[pump_error(PAC_pump_error_1,RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.4,RemoteIO1:4:I.Ch0OpenWire,P_PAC1_flow_err,P_PAC1_err,P_PAC1_maintain);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="40">
<![CDATA[pump_error(PAC_pump_error_2,RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.5,RemoteIO1:4:I.Ch1OpenWire,P_PAC2_flow_err,P_PAC2_err,P_PAC2_maintain);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="41">
<![CDATA[pump_error(PAC_pump_error_3,RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.6,RemoteIO1:4:I.Ch2OpenWire,P_PAC3_flow_err,P_PAC3_err,P_PAC3_maintain);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="42">
<![CDATA[pump_error(PAC_pump_error_4,RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.7,RemoteIO1:4:I.Ch3OpenWire,P_PAC4_flow_err,P_PAC4_err,P_PAC4_maintain);]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="43">
<![CDATA[(*P_PAC1_err:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.4;*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="44">
<![CDATA[(*P_PAC2_err:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.5;*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="45">
<![CDATA[(*P_PAC3_err:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.6;*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="46">
<![CDATA[(*P_PAC4_err:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.7;*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="47">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="48">
<![CDATA[(*数字泵故障复位*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="49">
<![CDATA[if P_PAC1_reset then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="50">
<![CDATA[	P_PAC1_maintain:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="51">
<![CDATA[	RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="52">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="53">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="54">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="55">
<![CDATA[if P_PAC2_reset then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="56">
<![CDATA[	P_PAC2_maintain:=0;	]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="57">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="58">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="59">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="60">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="61">
<![CDATA[if P_PAC3_reset then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="62">
<![CDATA[	P_PAC3_maintain:=0;	]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="63">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="64">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="65">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="66">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="67">
<![CDATA[if P_PAC4_reset then]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="68">
<![CDATA[	P_PAC4_maintain:=0;	]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="69">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=1;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="70">
<![CDATA[else]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="71">
<![CDATA[    RemoteIO1:4:O.WireOffReset:=0;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="72">
<![CDATA[end_if;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="73">
<![CDATA[]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="74">
<![CDATA[(*电动阀阀位反馈*)]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="75">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_01_open:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.8;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="76">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_01_close:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.9;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="77">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_02_open:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.10;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="78">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_02_close:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.11;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="79">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_03_open:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.12;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="80">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_03_close:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.13;]]>
</Line>
<Line Number="81">
<![CDATA[VE_PAC_04_open:=RemoteIO1:0:I.Data.14;]]>
