<Routine Name="tank_control_PAC" Type="RLL">
<Description>
<![CDATA[储液罐液位控制流程。
液位过高过低报警。
液位过高时关闭进液阀，防止储液罐过满；
液位过低时关闭出液阀，防止计量泵空吸。]]>
</Description>
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池（控制阀动作）]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_1,PAC_tank_level_8LT01,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_1,PAC_level_low_alarm_1,PAC_tank_standby[1]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#PAC池（控制阀动作）]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_2,PAC_tank_level_8LT02,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_2,PAC_level_low_alarm_2,PAC_tank_standby[2]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，远期规划，没有进液管和进液阀，进液阀输出有临时变量替代，实际安装后填入真正变量。（控制阀动作）]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_3,PAC_tank_level_8LT03,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_3,PAC_level_low_alarm_3,PAC_tank_standby[3]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，远期规划，没有进液管和进液阀，进液阀输出有临时变量替代，实际安装后填入真正变量。（控制阀动作）
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_control_4,PAC_tank_level_8LT04,PAC_level_high_setting,PAC_level_low_setting,PAC_level_high_alarm_4,PAC_level_low_alarm_4,PAC_tank_standby[4]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[1#PAC池，仅报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_alarm[0],PAC_tank_level_8LT01,PAC_high_level_alarm_setting,PAC_low_level_alarm_setting,PAC_level_high_only_alarm_1,PAC_level_low_only_alarm_1,PAC_tank_standby[1]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[2#PAC池，仅报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_alarm[1],PAC_tank_level_8LT02,PAC_high_level_alarm_setting,PAC_low_level_alarm_setting,PAC_level_high_only_alarm_2,PAC_level_low_only_alarm_2,PAC_tank_standby[2]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[3#PAC池，仅报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_alarm[2],PAC_tank_level_8LT03,PAC_high_level_alarm_setting,PAC_low_level_alarm_setting,PAC_level_high_only_alarm_3,PAC_level_low_only_alarm_3,PAC_tank_standby[3]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[4#PAC池，仅报警]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Tank_level(tank_alarm[3],PAC_tank_level_8LT04,PAC_high_level_alarm_setting,PAC_low_level_alarm_setting,PAC_level_high_only_alarm_4,PAC_level_low_only_alarm_4,PAC_tank_standby[4]);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
